title: Malaysian General Election: 5 takeaways for Singapore
title_page: Malaysian General Election: 5 takeaways for Singapore | The Straits Times
maintext:
SINGAPORE - Hot on the heels of the electoral "tsunami" that swept the six-decades-old ruling coalition in neighbouring Malaysia out of power, came questions from Singaporeans.
While observers up north are seized by the momentous change in their country, Singaporeans were asking: Will this happen here in the next one, or two or three elections?
